1
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,540
[Zhejiang Q81256]

2
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,120
I'm leaving now,

3
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,450
keep an eye on the store.

4
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,079
Xiaoyue.

5
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,320
Manager Fang.

6
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:37,200
Uncle.

7
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,640
Just this suit?

8
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:39,760
Yes,

9
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:42,280
it's Diandian's engagement party today.

10
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,079
Manager Fang,

11
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,800
this is my best suit.

12
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,340
It's quite expensive.

13
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,560
Manager Fang,

14
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,600
which car should I take?

15
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,240
Take the one in the back,

16
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,680
her father's car.

17
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,120
Okay,

18
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,180
see you in a bit.

19
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,010
See you soon.

20
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:54,690
My cousin

21
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,480
is waiting for me.

22
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:57,840
Let's go.

23
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,300
Come on,

24
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,000
let's get moving.

25
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,140
Hold it steady.

26
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,410
Don't put this sofa in the bedroom,

27
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,060
can we put it in the guest room?

28
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:35,490
Okay.

29
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:36,850
This way,

30
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,250
take it slow.

31
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:43,810
Careful.

32
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,180
Your paranoia is acting up again.

33
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,090
What's that?

34
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,080
Hyacinths.

35
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,410
They bloom only once a year,

36
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,920
for just about two weeks.

37
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:34,200
The rest of the time they look like this,

38
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,400
with long green leaves

39
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,840
that resemble water plants.

40
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:37,900
When do they bloom?

41
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:40,880
Everything's been moved.

42
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,360
Please go downstairs to sign the papers.

43
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:42,800
Okay.

44
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,120
I'll go sign them.

45
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:52,600
Where are the qipaos?

46
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:54,400
The ones my mother

47
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,370
made for Teacher Jia Sulan,

48
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,040
those two dresses?

49
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,840
They're in the fitting room downstairs.

50
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:01,240
Good.

51
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,580
Mom's health was deteriorating.

52
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,240
The year Leifeng Tower was rebuilt,

53
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,410
she passed away.

54
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,000
Mom told me

55
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:28,320
if one day she's no longer by my side,

56
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:33,050
it just means she's waiting for me in another dimension,

57
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,860
where there's another her and me.

58
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,010
I've finished my homework.

59
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,570
Teacher Jia has the same illness as my mom.

60
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,159
She's sick too.

61
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,480
After that performance,

62
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,580
she never showed up again.

63
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,000
Thank you.

64
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,930
You're welcome.

65
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,080
Xu Tian,

66
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,160
mom's here.

67
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:17,720
Diandian.

68
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,320
Diandian.

69
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:19,920
Mom.

70
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:20,920
Grandpa.

71
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,600
Don't all crowd here.

72
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,120
Come in.

73
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,280
Take a look at the new place.

74
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,340
Come on, everyone.

75
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,760
Dian Dian's father is here too,

76
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,160
waiting for us at the hotel.

77
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,960
No need to introduce Mr. Fang, right?

78
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:30,490
Mr. Fang.

79
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,159
Aren't you going to change how you address him?

80
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:34,920
In a couple of days when Dian Dian and Mr. Fang

81
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,040
return from Guangzhou,

82
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,640
you'll get your marriage certificate,

83
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,480
and we'll have the wedding banquet,

84
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,680
and celebrate properly.

85
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,480
That's right!

86
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,600
I'll pay for the banquet.

87
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,360
And there will be a dowry too.

88
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:44,890
Mr. Fang,

89
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:45,960
I should be the one

90
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:47,200
paying for the banquet.

91
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:49,000
It's not that much money anyway.

92
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,440
Let's not block the hallway,

93
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,840
go upstairs to see the new place,

94
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,880
and then head to the hotel for dinner.

95
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:55,480
Dian Dian,

96
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,320
please take

97
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,450
everyone upstairs.

98
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,700
Uncle, please go up first.

99
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,300
Finally, finally.

100
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,160
Big auntie, little auntie!

101
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,600
Little auntie loves Diandian the most.

102
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,240
Come on,

103
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,600
don't block the way. Go upstairs

104
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,730
and see the new room.

105
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:08,640
Be careful.

106
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,340
So annoying

107
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,180
with all these people.

108
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,330
They're all family.

109
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:20,840
Wait,

110
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,200
I'll take you

111
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,200
to get something.

112
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:24,920
What?

113
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:27,560
You'll see when we get there.

114
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:30,080
Tomorrow mom and I are going to Guangzhou.

115
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,040
I'll be back in three days,

116
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,570
but she'll stay for a month.

117
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:33,320
At the hotel,

118
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,650
mom wants to have a talk.

119
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,600
Should I come too?

120
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,460
It's not really a lecture,

121
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,809
just a heart-to-heart with us.

122
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,159
Well,

123
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,290
should I be nervous?

124
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,890
That's up to you.

125
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,410
Go upstairs and keep them company.

126
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,760
Stop it, stop it.

127
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,640
Let's talk business.

128
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,680
Yang Yun has already been

129
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:33,760
to the station for questioning,

130
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:35,420
what else is there to discuss?

131
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,520
Did you talk

132
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,080
with Yang Yun?

133
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,600
No.

134
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,720
You're the director,

135
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:42,850
a senior artist.

136
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,200
The direction of the show

137
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,860
should follow your guidance.

138
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,720
Senior.

139
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,130
That sounds creepy.

140
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,000
They

141
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,520
are all your juniors.

142
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,760
Yang Yun has recovered

143
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,360
and is full of energy.

144
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:58,580
The theater troupe

145
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:01,160
needs to decide whether to revive 'White Snake'

146
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,220
or produce 'Jin Se'

147
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,200
today.

148
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:05,720
"Jin Se"

149
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,090
You're new here?

150
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:11,760
You need to register your name and phone number to enter.

151
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,160
My name is Qiao Guanghui.

152
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:14,760
No exceptions.

153
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,760
This register used to be a mess,

154
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:18,000
I've organized it now.

155
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,260
Who are you here to see?

156
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,440
No manners,

157
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,250
making me register.

158
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,120
Li Shangyin's poem

159
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,520
"The Ornate Zither."

160
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:28,400
That's the name I've chosen for our new production.

161
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,680
We'll only perform

162
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:32,400
the "Broken Bridge" and "Boating on the Lake" scenes from "Legend of the White Snake."

163
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:35,120
The relationship between Bai Suzhen and Xiaoqing.

164
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:37,400
I mentioned it to you before the incident in October.

165
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,400
So you'll direct,

166
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,680
you'll choreograph,

167
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,260
right, Director Yang?

168
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,040
The bureau

169
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:42,960
is encouraging

170
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:45,020
the development of artistic talent.

171
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:49,060
Will Qiaomi still play Xiaoqing?

172
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,580
Will Yin Ye still play Xu Xian?

173
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,410
Do we still need Xu Xian?

174
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:58,000
We definitely need him, right?

175
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,260
What about Bai Suzhen?

176
00:10:59,400 --> 00:10:59,880
Me.

177
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,480
So

178
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,240
you write, direct, choreograph,

179
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,240
and perform.

180
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,160
If you've already decided everything,

181
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:08,000
then why are we

182
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,660
even having this meeting?

183
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,520
Let's vote by a show of hands.

184
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,250
Unanimously approved.

185
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,400
Only then will everyone be motivated.

186
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,840
The experienced should guide the newcomers,

187
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:19,900
and new productions need the director's guidance too.

188
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:22,200
Those in favor of restaging

189
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:25,300
"The Brocade Zither," raise your hands.

190
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,680
Where is Wen Xiaoyao?

191
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,880
Haven't heard from her these days.

192
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,440
The perfectly fine "Legend of the White Snake"

193
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,040
was ruined because of her, wasn't it?

194
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:45,400
Xiaoyao has already danced through three premiere performances

195
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:47,520
without any regard for her artistic career.

196
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:49,400
Please don't talk about careers.

197
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,640
I won't agree to this.

198
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:51,170
I object.

199
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,520
Even if objecting is useless, I still object.

200
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:55,240
Just go ahead with your rehearsal

201
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,370
I can't direct this.

202
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,250
Where's Xiaomi?

203
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,050
You must sign in.

204
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,560
Let go of me

205
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:09,520
did you hear me?

206
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,320
I'm in a hurry.

207
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:15,740
Tell this idiot to take his hands off.

208
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,100
Insisting I sign in

209
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,480
do you know who I am?

210
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,920
You still need to sign in.

211
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:22,020
Director Yang.

212
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:22,920
Director Qiao is here.

213
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:24,580
I'm here to pick up my daughter

214
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,200
where should I go?

215
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:28,200
Sign in.

216
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,040
Sign in.

217
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,000
To hell with your sign-in!

218
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:46,720
Sign here.

219
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,220
Information incomplete.

220
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:45,680
Xiao Yao,

221
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:47,760
today is the seventh day of the lunar month,

222
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:50,490
Dad's coming to take me to Babaoshan to visit Mom.

223
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:53,730
Thank you and Uncle Hui.

224
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,850
I live near Leifeng Pagoda,

225
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,420
tomorrow I'll go there

226
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,220
and pretend I'm visiting Mom.

227
00:14:05,920 --> 00:14:06,980
What are you doing?

228
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:09,600
Going to class

229
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,930
to teach children how to dance.

230
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,440
Let me tell you a joke.

231
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,410
When I was in school,

232
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,840
my dream was to become a scientist.

233
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,650
Then I realized,

234
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:41,050
some people wanted to be painters,

235
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,840
others wanted to be writers.

236
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,730
Do you know what my dream is now?

237
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:49,640
What?

238
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,660
To build a family with you.

239
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:58,970
Funny, isn't it?

240
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:33,440
Hello.

241
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:34,850
My name is Xu.

242
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,560
I ordered

243
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:37,280
a ring here earlier.

244
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,280
Please come this way.

245
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:47,600
When did you order it?

246
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:48,520
On the 10th

247
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:49,600
of last month.

248
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,200
Try it on.

249
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,400
We've already paid for it.

250
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:57,200
The deposit has been paid,

251
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:57,760
Mrs. Xu.

252
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,100
Why don't you try it on?

253
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:16,720
How is it,

254
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:17,840
Mrs. Xu? Does it fit?

255
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,120
I'm not Mrs. Xu yet.

256
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:23,720
Isn't it a bit too big?

257
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:25,860
It fits perfectly.

258
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,600
I think it's a bit big.

259
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:30,160
Please wait a moment,

260
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,420
I'll adjust it for you.

261
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:46,560
Isn't it too expensive?

262
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:47,720
Not at all,

263
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:49,490
it's once in a lifetime.

264
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:51,740
I should be the one paying.

265
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,600
Of course it should be me.

266
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,090
Let's return it.

267
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:56,680
Do you like it?

268
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:58,960
I do like it.

269
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,760
Come, Mrs. Xu,

270
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:00,820
try it on again.

271
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,280
Excuse me, I'd like to ask

272
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:10,200
if I can

273
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:12,800
return this?

274
00:17:14,280 --> 00:17:15,800
This is a custom-made item

275
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:16,859
I'm afraid not.

276
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:19,119
Can I exchange it for something else?

277
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:19,880
Yes, of course.

278
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,119
Please take a look at which style you'd prefer.

279
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:23,380
Maybe check these out.

280
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:24,690
This one.

281
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,490
This one.

282
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,250
This one.

283
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:29,370
And this one too.

284
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,540
Please take a look at all of these.

285
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:46,920
This one here,

286
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:48,440
simple yet elegant.

287
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:49,420
This one

288
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:51,810
can also be customized specially for you.

289
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:52,280
Look,

290
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,640
inside the ring,

291
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,320
we can engrave your names,

292
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,450
anniversary dates,

293
