00:32:57,640 --> 00:33:00,100
everything valuable is right here with you.

587
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:08,480
What are you doing?

588
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,480
Taking advantage of the situation.

589
00:33:10,800 --> 00:33:11,560
Come pick me up.

590
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:12,040
Can't do it,

591
00:33:12,040 --> 00:33:12,520
no car.

592
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:14,480
Then I'll come to you.

593
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:15,010
I'm busy,

594
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:19,800
we'll talk later.

595
00:33:31,080 --> 00:33:32,200
Stop looking.

596
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,960
I threw it in the river,

597
00:33:34,080 --> 00:33:35,320
not in the grass.

598
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:38,000
You're trying to scam me.

599
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:38,880
Just say the word

600
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:39,560
that I'm bothering you,

601
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:40,800
and I'll disappear immediately,

602
00:33:40,800 --> 00:33:41,730
clean and quick.

603
00:33:42,560 --> 00:33:43,760
Scamming people

604
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:44,960
isn't my style.

605
00:33:45,800 --> 00:33:47,130
I'm doing fine on my own.

606
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:49,840
Fine? What fine?

607
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:52,120
Look how thin your face is,

608
00:33:53,080 --> 00:33:54,280
like a crescent moon.

609
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,120
How could anyone not worry?

610
00:33:56,120 --> 00:33:57,980
I'm not in the mood for your jokes.

611
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:00,580
Actually, I'm quite enjoying

612
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,520
the way you are right now.

613
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:06,040
Enjoying?

614
00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:08,120
You used to always snap at me,

615
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,130
but now it's so nice.

616
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:12,370
You're like a piece of jade,

617
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,420
smooth and gentle.

618
00:34:16,080 --> 00:34:17,409
Did I used to snap at you?

619
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:19,940
You don't even realize it.

620
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:21,760
When I talked to you,

621
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:24,199
I had to switch my thinking eight different ways

622
00:34:24,199 --> 00:34:25,530
just to keep up with you.

623
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:27,409
Now it's so nice,

624
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:29,320
in the sunset,

625
00:34:30,639 --> 00:34:31,560
you're bending over

626
00:34:31,560 --> 00:34:32,520
in the grass,

627
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:34,290
looking for my car keys.

628
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,300
How beautiful.

629
00:34:36,159 --> 00:34:38,620
I should enjoy this illusion while it lasts.

630
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:41,080
If you ever snap out of it,

631
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:44,159
I'll probably be in trouble again.

632
00:34:44,159 --> 00:34:45,360
I won't snap out of it.

633
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:48,320
This river used to have

634
00:34:48,679 --> 00:34:49,800
so much water.

635
00:34:52,080 --> 00:34:52,610
How about

636
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:53,320
I take you out

637
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:54,600
for something delicious?

638
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:56,460
I'm talking about the river here.

639
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:58,280
Since you're not cooking anyway,

640
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,320
and it's getting cold,

641
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:00,920
you need to put on some weight.

642
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:02,480
I'll treat you to hot pot lamb.

643
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,210
How about it?

644
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:03,920
Or maybe

645
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,600
we could invite Brother Gang

646
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:06,480
to cheer you up.

647
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:10,170
What about the car keys?

648
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:12,800
There might be a spare at home.

649
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:19,920
In reality,

650
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:22,100
they're pushing me to the sidelines.

651
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,240
This is directly related

652
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:28,410
to Yaoyao's departure.

653
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:30,020
My debut was sensational,

654
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,920
all the southern orders came in.

655
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,060
National tour,

656
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:36,130
and now you've arranged for

657
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:38,960
Yang Yun to take my position.

658
00:36:04,800 --> 00:36:07,060
Zhou Tong knows best how to enjoy hotpot.

659
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,640
But these past two years.

660
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:14,720
I've eaten there with my son a few times.

661
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:16,330
Mr. Qiao.

662
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:17,920
Why don't you stop

663
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,580
that sponsorship for a while.

664
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:23,210
I think if I don't make some effort now,

665
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:25,400
they'll announce Yang Yun as the director

666
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:26,460
after the New Year.

667
00:36:28,680 --> 00:36:30,010
The newly arranged show

668
00:36:30,560 --> 00:36:32,820
is still 'The Legend of the White Snake.'

669
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:35,080
Do you know what it's called?

670
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,060
'The Brocade Zither.'

671
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,690
What are they thinking?

672
00:36:40,680 --> 00:36:41,480
Brother Gang,

673
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:42,920
tomorrow

674
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,360
you should go to

675
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,440
Jinsong Plaza.

676
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,160
Where is that?

677
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:51,340
The place where Guanwang dances.

678
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:54,720
I've been there once.

679
00:36:54,720 --> 00:36:55,320
What's up?

680
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:57,620
Lead the dance for the ladies,

681
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,050
show your professional skills

682
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:03,120
and liven up the atmosphere.

683
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:04,580
It would be best

684
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:06,440
if you could get Guanwang dancing too.

685
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:07,200
Go to hell!

686
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:13,880
My life is already at rock bottom

687
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:15,680
and it just keeps sinking lower.

688
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,260
What's so bad about it?

689
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,400
I'm not mad at you.

690
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:22,200
Just seeing your face makes my blood boil,

691
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:24,530
you look like you're asking for a beating.

692
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,220
I'm trying to respect you.

693
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:32,560
But you can't just keep bullying people like this.

694
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,600
People like you

695
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:36,980
deserve to be thrown straight into a hot pot.

696
00:37:39,040 --> 00:37:39,770
You see that?

697
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,000
That's just how she is.

698
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,260
That's exactly right.

699
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:44,040
I brought you here

700
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:46,500
just so she could give you a piece of her mind.

701
00:37:48,040 --> 00:37:49,300
Why should I take this?

702
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:52,530
I'm also a national first-class director

703
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:54,100
and a people's artist.

704
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:56,360
Yaoyao stopped performing

705
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:58,960
because she was heartbroken after my son died.

706
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:00,840
Your career slump

707
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,650
is because you're getting old,

708
00:38:02,680 --> 00:38:04,040
what's your excuse?

709
00:38:05,160 --> 00:38:06,920
Why blame Yaoyao?

710
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,920
What was that?

711
00:38:08,680 --> 00:38:09,610
Who was it again?

712
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:10,290
Yang Yun.

713
00:38:11,680 --> 00:38:12,240
Yang Yun,

714
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:14,520
don't like what you hear?

715
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:16,000
Why blame us women?

716
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:20,240
I told you to go to classes at Guanwang Entertainment,

717
00:38:20,240 --> 00:38:21,970
but you haven't gone even once.

718
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:27,100
Having you lead the dance for the girls is for your own good.

719
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:28,160
Step back,

720
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:29,720
so you can find

721
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,880
the right place in your life.

722
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:32,540
Enough,

723
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,930
no need to go to classes.

724
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,120
First floor, second floor,

725
00:38:36,120 --> 00:38:37,320
don't bother with any of it.

726
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,580
Better if it all fails.

727
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:39,480
Guanwang,

728
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:42,000
you need to pull yourself together.

729
00:38:42,160 --> 00:38:45,090
It doesn't matter if the business makes money or not,

730
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:46,540
but if it really fails,

731
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:48,050
you'll feel even worse.

732
00:38:48,200 --> 00:38:49,730
It'll fail sooner or later,

733
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:50,720
just like life.

734
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:51,720
No, no,

735
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:53,800
don't be so pessimistic.

736
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:56,280
Brother Gang at least

737
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:58,170
still has some influence left,

738
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,760
he's still carrying

739
00:39:00,160 --> 00:39:01,090
the dance troupe

740
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,560
director's prestige.

741
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:03,800
After a while,

742
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:05,880
once the retirement news gets out,

743
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:07,410
it won't be worth anything.

744
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,220
Qiao Guanghui,

745
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,080
whose side are you on?

746
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:14,480
Definitely not yours.

747
00:39:15,720 --> 00:39:17,580
Choosing women over friendship.

748
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:18,320
Thank you,

749
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,320
thank you for

750
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,120
pointing out

751
00:39:21,520 --> 00:39:22,320
the key point.

752
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:25,130
It would sound fake if I said it myself.

753
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:26,680
Did you hear that, Guanwang?

754
00:39:26,680 --> 00:39:27,080
There,

755
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:30,100
that's the kind of person I am.

756
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:32,640
Eat some more.

757
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,640
It's getting late, isn't it?

758
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:37,080
Got it.

759
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,560
You're really in a hurry.

760
00:39:48,560 --> 00:39:49,360
Don't mind me.

761
00:39:51,240 --> 00:39:52,900
I'm close with Director Yang.

762
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:54,900
I'll put in a good word for you.

763
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:56,520
Really?

764
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:57,880
Ignore me.

765
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:01,920
Look at you,

766
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:04,240
such a social climber.

767
00:40:08,520 --> 00:40:11,120
Then go take classes at Guanwang Entertainment.

768
00:40:11,120 --> 00:40:12,280
She doesn't need me.

769
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:15,260
Times like these are when she needs you most.

770
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:18,170
She lost her husband years ago,

771
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,440
and now her eldest son is gone too.

772
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:21,880
She must feel so lonely.

773
00:40:22,080 --> 00:40:23,080
She has you.

774
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:26,200
She needs you now.

775
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:28,400
What do you mean?

776
00:40:29,160 --> 00:40:30,600
Helping her is helping me,

777
00:40:30,600 --> 00:40:31,400
or we're done.

778
00:40:33,240 --> 00:40:35,240
You need to have some compassion.

779
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:36,940
Who has compassion for me?

780
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:38,920
Real men

781
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:40,600
don't need compassion,

782
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:42,760
we deserve whatever we get,

783
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:43,490
understand?

784
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:46,120
I'll go to Hangzhou tomorrow to find Yaoyao.

785
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:46,680
When?

786
00:40:48,760 --> 00:40:50,690
After you meet with Director Yang.

787
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:53,090
Director Yang can wait.

788
00:40:53,240 --> 00:40:54,080
He'll be fine.

789
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:56,200
You need to comfort Guanwang first.

790
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:00,690
Alright.

791
00:41:05,440 --> 00:41:06,600
When will you go?

792
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:08,420
First thing tomorrow.

793
00:41:08,480 --> 00:41:10,340
Then I'll go tomorrow afternoon.

794
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:15,120
Do you know what Yaoyao

795
00:41:15,120 --> 00:41:16,320
is doing in Hangzhou?

796
00:41:16,720 --> 00:41:19,840
Goodbye, teacher.

797
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:15,980
What are you doing?

798
00:42:23,080 --> 00:42:24,210
Who is Shi Diandian?

799
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:26,160
I checked the crew registry today,

800
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:28,760
she came to see you the day before the incident.

801
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:29,120
Dad said

802
00:42:29,120 --> 00:42:31,580
she was the one who took Tong to the hospital.

803
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:42,360
Was it her?

804
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:45,940
Is her contact information in the registry?

805
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:52,560
I'll check tomorrow.

806
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:57,120
Could you help me check now?

807
00:42:57,920 --> 00:42:58,480
Thanks.

808
00:43:51,960 --> 00:43:52,920
Production Manager

809
00:43:52,920 --> 00:43:54,180
Production Assistant

